dc_description_s: This data represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2023. [Point data at sections corners. Ongoing improvement program to meet 3rd order GPS accuracy standards. Coordinates not derived from GPS are from traditional survey methods, or in a few cases, map estimates.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://www.co.portage.wi.gov/375/Land-Information-GIS
